    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine sancte et individue trinitatis. <persName
                            key="#Imperial/royal_diploma #Emperor/king"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/7">Otto</persName> divina favente
                        misericordia Romanorum <rs key="#Emperor/king">imperator</rs> augustus. Iam
                        dudum omnia quae data sunt <orgName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/juridical_persons/81"
                            key="#Chancellor #Dioecesis #Plebs #Districtio #Mother_churches #Bishops #Archpriests"
                            >sancto Eusebio</orgName> confirmavimus, sed ea que sunt necessaria et
                        maxime ea que <persName ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/32"
                            key="#Emperor/king">Karulus</persName> imperator <persName
                            key="#Bishops" ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/33"
                            >Lituardo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopo</rs> aut dedit aut reddidit, iterum et iterum ex
                        nunc confirmamus et successores nostros idem agere rogamus, quia nos ipsi
                        imperatoris Karuli. <rs key="#Imperial/royal_diploma">precepta</rs> legimus
                        et litere in <rs key="#Mother_churches">ecclesia</rs> sancti Eusebii a
                        tempore Karuli super altare sancti Iohannis baptiste scripte testimonium
                        donant et ad veritatem recognoscendam fidem legentibus faciunt, id est <rs
                            key="#Teloneum">toloneum</rs> et <rs key="#Districtio">districtum</rs>
                        suarum <rs key="#Plebs">plebium</rs> et super sua <rs key="#Casali"
                            >habitancium</rs>, <rs key="#Rivers #Fluvial_transport">aquam de
                            Scicida</rs>, aquam de Saruo, aquam de Eleuo cum utrisque ripis a loco
                        ubi nascuntur, usque in Padum, aquam de Pado cum duabus rippis a
                            <placeName>Lionna</placeName> usque <orgName key="#Plebs">plebem
                            Martori</orgName>, aquam de Duria cum utrisque ripis a <placeName>Petra
                            grossa </placeName>usque<placeName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/183">Verucham.</placeName>
                        Confirmamus <placeName>Malascum</placeName>, <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/estates/96"><placeName
                                ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/99"
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                >Firminianam</placeName></geogName>, <placeName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/51"><geogName
                                ref="#http://137.204.128.125/estates/63"
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                >Sestignum</geogName></placeName>, <geogName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/estates/41"
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ><placeName ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/3"
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                >Carexianam</placeName></geogName> cum utraque ripa, <placeName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/50"
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ><geogName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Castle"
                                ref="#http://137.204.128.125/estates/62"
                            >Buiellam</geogName></placeName> cum omnibus suis appendiciis,
                            <placeName ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/206"
                            >Galianicum</placeName><placeName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/208">Ponderanam</placeName>,
                            <placeName>Mulinariam</placeName>, <placeName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/210">Andornum</placeName>,
                            <placeName>Causades</placeName>, montem <placeName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/211">Cisidola</placeName>,
                            <placeName>Pedroro</placeName>, <placeName>Blatini</placeName>,
                            <placeName>Beduluum</placeName> et <placeName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/212">Clauaziam</placeName>,
                            <placeName ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/213">Candele</placeName>
                        et <placeName ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/214">Cliuoli</placeName>
                        quia <persName ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/21" key="#Emperor/king"
                            >Berengarius</persName> et <persName>Albertus</persName> reges quorum
                            <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >proprietates</rs> fuerunt, ei dederunt, <placeName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/215">Treuerem</placeName> et
                        districtum per totum Buiellensem et <placeName>Calaniago</placeName>,
                            <placeName>Redigada</placeName>, <placeName>Readigadella</placeName>,
                            <placeName>Trebledo</placeName>, <placeName>Orco</placeName>, vallem
                            <placeName ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/103">Cledi</placeName>,
                            <placeName key="#Gualdi">Walda</placeName>. Damus omnia predia
                            <persName>Ardoini</persName> filii <persName>Daidonis</persName>, quia
                        hostis publicus adiudicatus episcopum <persName>Petrum</persName>
                        <placeName>Vercellensem</placeName> interfecit et interfectum incendere non
                        expavit, et predia eorum qui exploratu armis et ipsis manibus huic
                        crudelitati interfuerunt, id est filiorum <persName>Teperti</persName> de
                            <placeName>Cassale</placeName>
                        <persName>Goslini</persName>, <persName>Aimini</persName> de
                            <placeName>Liuurno</placeName>, <persName>Alberti</persName> et
                            <persName>Gribaldi</persName> de <placeName>Vnglano</placeName>. Damus
                        predia illorum qui cum armis ecclesiam sancti Eusebii vastaverunt, id est
                            <persName>Olrici</persName> de <placeName>Bayna</placeName>,
                            <persName>Roderardi</persName> de <placeName>Sandiliano</placeName>,
                            <persName>Arderici</persName> de <placeName>Magnanigulo</placeName>, <rs
                            key="#Slave">servi</rs> sancti Eusebii, <persName>Alberti</persName> et
                            <persName>Vilielmi</persName> de <placeName>Saluciola</placeName>,
                            <persName>Astulfi</persName> et fratrum eius de
                            <placeName>Vualdingo</placeName>, <persName>Vghonis</persName> de
                            <placeName>Palestre</placeName>, Stephani de Cliuolo, Ademari de
                        Gambolade, Vgonis de Ciriago, Aldonis de Leuriana, Ysac et fratris eius.
                        Confirmamus <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Forests #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/estates/127"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/216"
                            >Sulciam</placeName></geogName> cum silva <placeName
                            key="#Curtes #Forests">Salsa</placeName>, <rs key="#Castle"
                            >castellum</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Castle">Uictimuli</placeName>, <rs key="#Local_markets"
                            >mercatum</rs> et districtum <orgName key="#Subdeacons">plebis
                                <placeName key="#Local_markets #Districtio">sancte
                                Aghate</placeName></orgName> et <rs key="#Curtes">curtis</rs> de
                            <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/estates/97"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/101"
                            >Asiliano</placeName></geogName> et in <placeName>Tronciano</placeName>
                        et in altero <placeName ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/218"
                            >Tronziano</placeName> et per totam campaniam et castrum <placeName
                            key="#Castle" ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/218"
                            >Quirini</placeName>. Damus predia <persName key="#Subdeacons"
                            >Agadi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Subdeacons">subdiaconi</rs> de <placeName>sancta
                            Aghata</placeName>, <persName>Goslini</persName>,
                            <persName>Constancii</persName>, <persName>Guidonis</persName>,
                            <persName>Eurardi</persName>, <persName>Amizonis</persName> fratris
                            <persName>Gunterii</persName>. Confirmamus sanctam Mariam Moliade que
                        dicitur <placeName>Monasteriolum</placeName>, cum sua pertinentia, cum
                            <placeName ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/219">Bornade</placeName>
                        et <placeName>Grignasco</placeName> et <rs>districtu</rs>
                        <placeName>vallis Scicide</placeName> et <rs>erimannos</rs> de
                            <placeName>Nauola</placeName> et de Cassaliclo et <placeName
                            key="#Forests" ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/96">sciluam
                            Rouaxindam</placeName>; damus <placeName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/190" key="#Districtio"
                            >Gatinariam</placeName> cum districtu et omnia predia <persName
                            key="#Archdeacons">Gisalberti</persName>
                        <rs key="#Archdeacons">archidiaconi</rs> Vercellensis, et hoc iuste quia,
                        cum esset de familia sancti Eusebii, inflatus divitiis ecclesie ecclesiam
                        Vercellensem dominam suam fugit eamque cum <persName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/172">Ardoino</persName>
                        miserabiliter vastavit; similiter damus predia suorum generorum, id est
                            <persName>Vuilimanni </persName>de <placeName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/221">Causade </placeName>et
                            <persName>Vgonis</persName> de <placeName>Rade</placeName> et predia
                        parentum eius servorum fugitivorum, id est <persName>Liprandi</persName> et
                            <persName>Hermanni</persName> fratrum et <persName>Giselberti</persName>
                        iudicis. Districtum et teloneum in <placeName key="#Teloneum #Districtio"
                            >Rade</placeName>, <placeName key="#Teloneum #Districtio"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/222">Gislaringo</placeName>,
                            <placeName key="#Teloneum #Districtio"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/223">Arbori</placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Teloneum #Districtio" ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/30"
                            >Gregi</placeName>, <placeName key="#Teloneum #Districtio"
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/places/225">Albano</placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Teloneum #Districtio">Conflencia</placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Districtio">Odonicum</placeName> cum districtu reddimus et
                            <orgName>ecclesiam sancti Salvatoris </orgName>ultra Padum sicut Karulus
                        augustus fecit, confirmamus. Montem Pedogletum et
                            <placeName>Brosule</placeName> et districtum in
                            <placeName>Palazolo</placeName>, <placeName>Gorzano</placeName>,
                            <placeName>Liuagi</placeName>, <placeName>Gabiano</placeName>,
                            <placeName>Cantauenna</placeName>, <placeName>Carderisi</placeName>,
                            <placeName>Vliaco</placeName>,<placeName> Malione</placeName>,
                            <placeName>Azellii</placeName>, <placeName>Medule</placeName>,
                            <placeName>Herbara</placeName> confirmamus. Districtum <placeName>sancti
                            Euaxii </placeName>a Pado usque in Sturam, in
                            <placeName>Fraxaneto</placeName>, <placeName>Paxiliano</placeName>,
                        Ticinesse, <placeName>Sarmaza</placeName> et <orgName>sancto
                            Georgio</orgName> et in <placeName>Ozano</placeName> ultra tria
                        miliaria, predia <persName>Alberici</persName> de Monterone,
                            <persName>Milonis</persName> de Salerana, <persName>Tedisi </persName>de
                        Lauagna, <persName>Disonis</persName> de Vacaria,
                            <persName>Hermanni</persName> iudicis <persName>Graseuerti</persName> de
                        Cirisudo et fratrum eius, Cerrocaualli, castellum <placeName key="#Castle"
                            >sancti Angeli</placeName> in Lacu maiore,<orgName> abbaciam de
                                <placeName>Arona</placeName>
                        </orgName>confirmamus sicut preceptum Karuli testatur;
                            <placeName>Cerretum</placeName>, <placeName>Vulpara</placeName>,
                            <placeName>Cassanoua</placeName>, curticellem in <placeName>Bremide
                        </placeName>confirmamus, quia propria fuerunt Albani servi sancti Eusebii de
                        plebe Buiella; cortem <geogName>Torcelli</geogName> confirmamus sicut
                            <persName ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/12" key="#Emperor/king"
                            >Liprandus</persName> rex donavit; cortem <geogName>Canauam</geogName>
                        reddimus sicuti <persName>Ludouicus</persName> imperator donavit. Damus
                        autem sancto Eusebio omnia predia <persName key="#Archpriests"
                            >Cuniberti</persName> archipresbiteri et hoc iuste et rationabiliter,
                        quia omnia que de bonis ecclesie exierunt, iudicio ecclesie et seculi ad
                        ecclesiam cuius fuerunt, pertinebunt. Confirmamus sancto Eusebio
                            <orgName>abbaciam de <placeName>Luceio</placeName></orgName> sicuti
                        Karulus augustus et dive memorie genitor noster fecerunt; confirmamus
                            <orgName>sancto Michaeli de Loceio</orgName> hanc pertinenciam quam
                        Ortum sancti Michaelis vocamus, id est a Monte regis usque Aquam nigram
                        sicut currit Ampori, et usque Solarium arsum et usque fossatum Axinarium et
                        sicut est <orgName>ecclesia sancte Marie </orgName>a Ponte et Stura currit
                        subtus Broilum vetus; confirmamus <placeName>Aleram</placeName> usque
                        Gardinam et usque Ronchum sichum et a Terra monacorum sicut Ampori tenet,
                        usque in caput montis Salacesse et usque in Padum; confirmamus
                            <placeName>Camassa</placeName> nigra et totum Versare usque in Ampori et
                        totum Andolinum intra Duriam et Padum et Zebadasco; confirmamus sancto
                        Michaeli de Lozaio sicut <persName ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/9"
                            key="#Emperor/king">Lotarius</persName> augustus donavit, quando corpus
                        sancti Ianuarii ibi collocavit, cortem<geogName> Guadradula </geogName>cum
                        districtu herimannorum et teloneo et aquam Padi a portu Cleuasi cum utrisque
                        rippis usque ad Clerum ubi vetus Duria intrat in Padum et a Clero usque
                        Mundine et Marnunca, scilvam de Loceio et <placeName>Ronchum
                            sichum</placeName> et <placeName>Conzuningun</placeName> et scilvam
                            <placeName key="#Forests">Palazolascam</placeName> confirmamus sancto
                        Eusebio sicut ab antiquis semper pertinuit. Confirmamus <geogName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/estates/88"
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Alienations #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Romanianum</geogName>, <geogName
                            ref="#http://137.204.128.125/estates/98"
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Alienations #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Aucimianum</geogName> sicut Karulus augustus donavit et confirmavit.
                        Quod ut credatur et conservetur, hoc preceptum manu nostra firmavimus et
                        amore <persName key="#Bishops" ref="#http://137.204.128.125/people/171"
                            >Leonis</persName> episcopi qui nobis fidei testimonio aureus est, aureo
                        sigillo nostro iussimus insigniri. Signum domni Ottonis gloriosissimi (M.)
                        Romanorum imperatoris augusti. <persName>Heribertus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">canzellarius</rs> vice Petri Cumani episcopi et
                        archicanzellarii recognovit. Data non. maii anno dominice incarnationis
                        DCCCCXCVIIII, indictione XII, anno tercii Ottonis regnantis XV, imperii III;
                        actum Rome; feliciter amen. </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
